description: After an easy calamari recipe? You'll be enjoying this simple crumbed calamari with tasty miso-flavoured mayonnaise in 25 minutes.
name: Crumbed Calamari With Miso Mayonnaise Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Combine mayonnaise and miso paste in a small bowl. Scatter onion over calamari, then serve with miso mayonnaise and lemon cheeks.
